description:
&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen on Ward 35 Oncology to appoint a Clinical Sister/Charge Nurse.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ward 35 is a 30 bedded ward looking after patients with a variety of oncological conditions, including receiving inpatient chemotherapy and other specialist treatments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Successful candidates must be able to demonstrate excellent communication, management support, leadership skills and be fully competent in the delivery of Systemic Anti Cancer Treatments. The successful candidate must be highly motivated, innovative and able to take charge of our inpatient oncology ward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name- Emma Russell&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title- Modern Matron&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address- emma.russell3@uhcw.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
